01:42:50.360 --> 01:42:53.360
There are a lot of games you can play.

01:42:53.360 --> 01:42:58.080
So you're right the fact that you remember nothing after that anesthesia doesn't mean

01:42:58.080 --> 01:43:00.480
you weren't fully aware at that moment.

01:43:00.480 --> 01:43:04.840
