01:45:25.960 --> 01:45:30.920
variety, but certainly not as exhausting all of consciousness.

01:45:30.920 --> 01:45:36.920
And it might even be on this view that, for example, a dog or a mouse might have primary

01:45:36.920 --> 01:45:42.120
